      <title>据称，中国 Hithium 明年将在香港进行 5 亿美元 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-s-hithium-is-said-to-weigh-500-million-hk-ipo-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，厦门海氢储能科技股份有限公司正考虑最早于明年在香港进行首次公开​​募股 (IPO)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-s-hithium-is-said-to-weigh-500-million-hk-ipo-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 04:40:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大皇家银行财富管理公司“增持”美国股票和黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/rbc-wealth-management-is-overweight-us-stocks-gold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行财富管理亚洲区高级投资策略师 Jasmine Duan 谈到了共和党领导的众议院否决由当选总统唐纳德·特朗普支持的临时融资计划、美联储政策及其对金融市场的影响。她还解释了她为什么青睐黄金。她在“彭博：亚洲交易”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/rbc-wealth-management-is-overweight-us-stocks-gold</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 03:58:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国一年期债券收益率自 2009 年以来首次降至 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-one-year-yield-sinks-toward-1-as-policy-easing-bets-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员加大对进一步放松货币政策的押注，且投资者寻求避险资产，中国一年期债券收益率自全球金融危机以来首次下滑至 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-one-year-yield-sinks-toward-1-as-policy-easing-bets-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 01:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
